Package: xvalidation
Title: Set of easy functions to perform cross-validation.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 'Leonardo Di Donato <leodidonato@gmail.com> [aut,cre]'
Description: xvalidation provides a set of simple but effective functions
    to perform cross-validation of your model on your dataset.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    assertthat
License: GPL-3
Suggests:
    devtools
Collate:
    'xvalidation-package.r'
    'cross-validation.r'
    'handlers.r'
